* create private domain doesn't fail when domain already exists by @Benjamintf1 in https://github.com/cloudfoundry/cli/pull/2609
* feat: add tip to restart app when enabling ssh  (v7) by @wanddynosios in https://github.com/cloudfoundry/cli/pull/2360
* Bump aws-actions/configure-aws-credentials from 3 to 4 by @dependabot in https://github.com/cloudfoundry/cli/pull/2614
* Bump actions/download-artifact from 2 to 3 by @dependabot in https://github.com/cloudfoundry/cli/pull/2613
* Bump github/codeql-action from 1 to 2 by @dependabot in https://github.com/cloudfoundry/cli/pull/2621
* Bump actions/cache from 2 to 3 by @dependabot in https://github.com/cloudfoundry/cli/pull/2620
